..Objectives/eesmärkid:  To support students to become teachers who are able to create a safe, inclusive as well as stimulating learning environment by integrating both traditional and modern teaching resources, and materials (including digital technology).Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  On completion of the course students: 1) know the features of the modern learning environment and can describe them. 2) can analyse to which extent the learning environment is open and supports self-management and cooperation; 3) are able to find learning resources related to the teaching of their specialty and are able to point out the strengths and weaknesses of the learning materials found; 4) can create modern and suitable learning resources bank based on contemporary learning approach.
